PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Diallo CORLEY, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 155276
COA: 328532 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 19, 2018

Order

Stephen J. Markman, Chief Justice
